#
# $Id$
#
# Various URI checks
#

Module depends on: a dabase module

Exported Parameters:
-------------------

Name:    db_url
Type:    str
Default: "sql://serro:47serro11@localhost/ser"
Desc:    URL of the database to be used

Name:    uri_table
Type:    str
Default: "uri"
Desc:    Table containing list of allowed URIs
         for each user.

Name:    uri_user_column
Type:    str
Default: "username"
Desc:    Column holding usernames in the URI table

Name:    uri_domain_column
Type:    str
Default: "domain"
Desc:    Column holding domain in the URI table

Name:    uri_uriuser_column
Type:    str
Default: "uri_user"
Desc:    Column holding uri username in the URI table

Name:    subscriber_table
Type:    str
Default: "subscriber"
Desc:    Name of the subscriber table

Name:    subscriber_user_column
Type:    str
Default: "username"
Desc:    Column holding username in subscriber table

Name:    subscriber_domain_column
Type:    str
Default: "domain"
Desc:    Column hodling domains in the subscriber table


Exported Functions:
------------------

Name:   is_user
Params: username
Desc:   Check if the username in credentials matches
        the given username

Name:   check_to
Params: -
Desc:   Check To username against URI table or digest
        credentials
	
Name:   check_from
Params: -
Desc:   Check From username against URI table or digest
        credentials
	
Name:   does_uri_exist
Params: -
Desc:   Check if username in the request URI belongs to an
        existing user
